text: Ivan Ananyevich Lukyanov (; born 27 December 1990) is a Russian football player. ==Club career== He made his professional debut for FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny on 4 April 2011 in a Russian Football National League game against FC Luch-Energiya Vladivostok. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:People from Gornomariysky District Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Association football forwards Category:FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny players Category:FC Tyumen players Category:FC Volga Nizhny Novgorod players Category:FC Mordovia Saransk players Category:FC Tekstilshchik Ivanovo players Category:FC Chernomorets Novorossiysk players Category:Sportspeople from Mari El
